highlights.text: “That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 17 weeks straight.
Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “HUMBLE.” is the highest at #1.
“Unforgettable” by French Montana and Swae Lee is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 77 spots at #87.
“DNA.” by Kendrick Lamar is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
